[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說除蓋障菩薩所問經卷第十",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譯經三藏朝散大夫試鴻臚卿",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "光梵大師賜紫沙門臣惟淨等奉　詔譯爾時，除蓋障菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b17_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b17_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此法云何能證？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何能解？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b18_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b18_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b18_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "出世間慧，乃能證入內自明解。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b19_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」除蓋障菩薩言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「豈非慧證，即是自心內解入邪？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b20_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不也。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b20_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b20_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b20_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "慧但如實能觀諸法，由身作證故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b21_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」除蓋障菩薩言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若諸善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "豈非以彼聞思修慧能證法時，便能內自得解入邪？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b23_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b23_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不也。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b23_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b23_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "非彼聞思修慧纔得聞時，便能內自解入。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b24_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今當以譬喻略明斯義。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b25_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b25_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如大曠野中夏盛熱時，或有一人自東而西，復有一人自西而東，當其炎毒渴乏所逼，時西至人謂東來者：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b28_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我今極熱為渴所逼，汝所從來善履途道，何處當有流泉池沼清冷之水？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731b29_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願為我說，令我飲之除其渴惱。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c01_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』其東來者，善知東方所有道路，亦復悉知有水之處，其味甘美及深淺等，即告之云：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c03_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『汝今前去，當觀一處有二道路，出於左者不應當詣，由於右者汝可往之。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c04_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼有園林蒼翠滋茂，中有池沼，清流甘美衍漾彌滿。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c06_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c06_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於汝意云何？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c06_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼渴乏人纔聞說示有妙池沼起思念時，便能除去渴惱之患，即能內自得清涼邪？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c08_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」除蓋障菩薩言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c08_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不也。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c08_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而炎渴人，若親詣彼有水之處，於其池中飲其水已，是人乃能除去炎渴內自清涼。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c11_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聞思修慧非纔得聞便能內自解入法性，亦復如是。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c12_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝今當知，大曠野者是生死境；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夏盛熱時受炎渴人，即是一切諸有情類；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c14_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "極炎熾者，即是煩惱六塵愛境；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c14_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善知路人，即諸菩薩善能知於一切智道；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c15_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其飲水者即是內自入證解者，得法勝味輕清甘美，第一義諦諸法實性。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c17_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c17_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝今當聽，復說譬喻。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使如來住壽一劫，於閻浮提一切人前，稱讚天蘇陀妙色妙香，最上清淨精美之味，其所飲者得妙樂觸。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c20_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c20_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "閻浮提人聞如是說，於色香等內了知邪？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c21_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」除蓋障菩薩言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c21_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不也。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c22_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由是之故，當知聞思修慧非纔聞時便能內自解入法性。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c23_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝今復聽，譬若有人於果實中知一果名，自先食已，與未食人說其果味及色香等。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c25_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c25_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於汝意云何？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼未食人而能了知其果味邪？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c26_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」除蓋障菩薩言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不也。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c27_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c27_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c27_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c27_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由是之故，當知聞思修慧非纔聞時便能內自解入法性。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c28_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，除蓋障菩薩前白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c29_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善說世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0731c29_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善說善逝！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是內證理法，若有善男子能一歷耳，當知是人即能具足聞思修法。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a02_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a02_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人已具不顛倒因，故得此法。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a03_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a03_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如是，如是。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a03_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即得善解法界之理。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a05_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a05_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，善知空境界。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a06_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、知力空；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a06_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、知無畏空；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、知不共佛法空；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a07_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、知戒蘊空；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a07_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、知定蘊空；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、知慧蘊空；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a08_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、知解脫蘊空；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、知解脫知見蘊空；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a09_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、知空空；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a09_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、知勝義空。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖知是空，亦不以其空因緣故，而於彼空有所得相，亦不執空，不起空見，不依止空，復不以其空因緣故，墮於斷見。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a12_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即善知空境界。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a13_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a14_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，即能善修無相之行。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a15_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a15_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、離外相；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a15_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、離內相；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a15_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、離戲論相；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a16_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、離一切遍計相；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a16_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、離一切有所得相；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a17_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、離一切舉動相；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a17_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、離一切虛假相；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a18_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、離一切所緣相；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a18_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、離識有得相；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、離識所知境相。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a19_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即能善修無相之行。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a20_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，除蓋障菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a21_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a21_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是行相是菩薩修無相之行。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a22_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何復見如來所修？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a22_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a22_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a23_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知此是不思議處。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a23_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a23_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "離心境界故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切有情若謂如來有所思者，彼即狂亂。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所有如來，若此岸事、若彼岸事，乃至疲極終不可見，亦不可得。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a26_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a26_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來之法不可思議，甚深難測，莫究其際，與虛空等，超出一切尋伺境界，超出一切有所得相，非諸惟忖較計度量之所能及。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732a29_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」除蓋障菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b01_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我有少疑欲伸請問，若如來、應供、正等正覺，見聽我問，願為略說。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b02_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b02_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「除蓋障！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b02_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝今當問斯為常事。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b03_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」除蓋障菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b03_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸有自高之者乃非正士，如何世尊為大法王，今自讚說，得非自高邪？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b05_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善哉！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b05_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善哉！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b05_24",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b06_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而汝心志深固能發是問，汝應諦聽，極善作意，今為汝說。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b07_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時除蓋障菩薩受教而聽。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b08_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b08_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來無我慢心亦不自高，不為利養名稱所欲生於我慢，亦不為求人所知故，亦不起於諂誑心故生於我慢，但以己所得法，廣為利益安樂一切有情。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b11_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b11_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "欲令有情於如來所發生清淨歡喜之心，堪任法器者令彼獲得一切善法，使其長夜得大利樂。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」除蓋障菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b14_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b14_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何有情而不能知如來勝德？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b15_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b15_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b15_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼實不知。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b15_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b16_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此佛剎中諸有情類，信解狹劣志著麁弊，少慧少信善根微尠，而不能知如來勝德，是故如來乃自讚說所有功德，意欲令諸有情發生淨信，能成如來諸勝功德。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b19_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b19_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如有人為大醫師，善療眾病，國中第一無有倫比，然其國中不知是人，明善方藥具醫勝德。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時彼醫師，見有疾苦所逼惱者即起是念：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b22_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『是人疾苦不善方藥，我今應當為其治療。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b23_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』是時，醫師詣病人所語其人言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b24_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我是醫師，明練方術，善知眾病及病所因，汝之病惱善為治療。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b25_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』時彼病人聞是言已，即於醫師起信重心而作依仗。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "醫師即時為其治療，病得除愈。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b27_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b27_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於汝意云何？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b28_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而彼醫師於病人前說已能解，為自讚邪？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b29_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」除蓋障菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b29_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不也。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b29_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732b29_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來亦復如是，為大醫王，善療有情諸煩惱病，知病所因施大法藥，而諸有情為無明等諸煩惱病之所逼迫，如來見已即詣其前，稱說如來具勝功德。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c04_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "令諸有情為其病苦所逼惱者，聞說如來勝功德已，能生清淨信重之心，以佛如來而為依仗。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c06_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來勝大醫王，為彼病者施大法藥，使諸有情煩惱重病咸得銷滅。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c08_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等是大法藥？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c08_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂多貪有情作不淨觀，多瞋有情作慈悲觀，愚癡有情作緣生觀。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c10_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以是緣故，乃見如來自讚勝德。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c11_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，得諸願離著。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c12_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、雖行布施而有願求，亦不著於布施；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c13_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、雖持禁戒，亦不著於持戒；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、雖行忍辱，亦不著於忍辱；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c14_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、雖起精進，亦不著於精進；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c15_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、雖習禪定，亦不著於禪定；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c16_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、雖修智慧，亦不著於智慧；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c16_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、雖依三界，亦不著於三界；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c17_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、雖求菩提，亦不著於菩提；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c18_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、雖行正道，亦不著於正道；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c18_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、雖入涅槃，亦不著於涅槃。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c19_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c19_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩離諸所著，雖於世間一切所行而悉無著。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c20_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即得諸願離著。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c22_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，得慈身具足。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、無方分慈；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c23_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、無種類慈；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、法慈；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c24_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、定慈；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c24_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、不害慈；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c24_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、利益慈；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、於一切有情平等心慈；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c25_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、等心無瞋恚慈；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c26_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、周遍十方廣大慈；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c26_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、出世間慈。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c27_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即得慈身具足。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c28_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，得悲身具足。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c29_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0732c29_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、見諸苦惱無救無依無歸趣者，菩薩見已發起菩提心；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a01_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、發菩提心已求所得法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a02_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、歷苦勤求得法成已，普為有情作大利益；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a03_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、慳貪有情令行布施；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a04_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、毀戒有情令持淨戒；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a04_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、瞋心有情令修忍行；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a05_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、懈怠有情令發精進；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a05_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、散亂有情令住定心；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a06_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、無智有情令修智慧；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、菩薩為利有情故，不以艱苦壞失退轉菩提勝行。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a08_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即得悲身具足。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a09_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a09_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，善修喜行。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a10_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a10_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、菩薩自得出離三有熾然，故生歡喜；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a11_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、為斷長時輪迴往來繫縛之索，故生歡喜；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a12_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、菩薩遠離種種尋求，自已得渡生死海中諸惡雜類，故生歡喜；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、菩薩自已摧折久遠以來高慢之幢，故生歡喜；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a15_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、菩薩以智金剛，自已摧碎煩惱高峯細無塵末，故生歡喜；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a16_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、菩薩自得安隱亦復令他悉得安隱，故生歡喜；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a17_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、菩薩於其世間，貪愛執縛暗瞑所覆不得自在，長眠境中自能醒然睡眼明已，亦復令他悉能開覺，故生歡喜；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a20_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、菩薩自能解脫出離惡趣，亦復令他悉得解脫出離惡趣，故生歡喜；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a22_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、有情久處生死曠野險難之中，獨行無侶周旋往返，不知其道不識方所，菩薩自能超出遠離，而悉為他指導開示，故生歡喜；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a25_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、菩薩得近一切智城，故生歡喜。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a25_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a26_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即善修喜行。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a27_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a27_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，即善修捨行。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a28_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a28_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、眼雖觀色而行捨行，亦不見眼識色境，若增若減，若成若壞；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733a29_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、耳雖聽聲，三者、鼻雖嗅香，四者、舌雖了味，五者、身雖覺觸，六者、意雖知法而行捨行，亦復不見耳聲、鼻香、舌味、身觸、意法諸塵，若增若減，若成若壞；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、雖觀行苦而行捨行，亦不見行苦，若增若減，若成若壞；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b05_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、雖觀苦苦而行捨行，亦不見苦苦，若增若減，若成若壞；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b06_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、雖觀壞苦而行捨行，亦不見壞苦，若增若減，若成若壞；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、觀所作已辦有情，菩薩於彼生歡喜心，乃起是念：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b09_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我欲度彼，彼已自度。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b09_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』故修捨行。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b10_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即善修捨行。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b11_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b11_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，即得神通游戲。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b12_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b12_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、示現捨壽；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、入胎受生；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b13_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、現童子相宮中游戲；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b13_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、出家；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b14_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、苦行；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b14_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、詣菩提場；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b14_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、成等正覺降伏魔軍；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b15_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、現寂靜相；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b15_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、轉妙法輪；",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、入大涅槃。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b16_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，除蓋障菩薩前白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b17_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b17_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何因緣故，菩薩示現兜率陀天捨壽，乃至示現入大涅槃？",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b19_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b19_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b19_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "兜率陀天諸有情等多生常想，而彼有情見菩薩——於一切世間最上、最勝，而復高顯，觀者無厭，不為五欲境界所染——能起捨壽，而彼有情見已，轉於常想，生無常想，由依止無常故，即起不放逸行。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b23_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又復有情起放逸心者，於菩薩所雖有愛樂信重之心，然於諸境生愛著故，於菩薩所不來親近恭敬承事，而彼有情乃起是念：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b26_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『菩薩久住於此，我亦久住。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』生放逸心。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733b27_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩為欲令彼有情起於厭離得不放逸，由能不起放逸心故，即得不退轉於阿耨多羅三藐三菩提，菩薩以是緣故，於兜率陀天示現捨壽。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733c01_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733c01_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有有情應以入胎受生而可度者，菩薩即現入胎受生之相，令其見已生希有心。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733c03_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩處母胎中，為彼彼有情如應說法，令得不退轉於阿耨多羅三藐三菩提，菩薩以是緣故，示現受生。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733c05_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733c06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有有情應以童子宮中游戲之相而可度者，又以下劣信解諸有情類，菩薩為成熟故為護持故，乃現童子宮中游戲之相。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733c08_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733c09_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有有情應以出家之相而可度者，菩薩為成熟故，乃現出家之相。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733c10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733c10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有志著麁弊天、龍、夜叉、乾闥婆、阿修羅等，應以苦行之相而可度者，菩薩為欲成熟彼故，及為降伏諸外道故，乃現苦行之相。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733c13_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733c13_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有有情於長時中，念求菩薩當於何時詣菩提場，我當隨應作供養事。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733c15_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩為欲成熟彼有情故，即為示現詣菩提場。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733c16_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "至菩提場已，令諸有情隨應供養，作供養已，而彼有情即得不退轉於阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733c18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733c18_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有有情自恃我慢貢高，菩薩為欲令彼轉於我慢心故，現坐道場成等正覺降伏魔軍。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733c20_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復為有情樂寂靜者，便謂獲得勝上所證，菩薩乃為示現成等正覺。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733c22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩成正覺時，三千大千世界種種音聲皆悉寂然，而彼樂寂有情見是三千大千世界皆寂然已，俱發願言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733c24_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『願我亦復如是，得成阿耨多羅三藐三菩提果。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733c25_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733c26_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有有情樂為師尊專志願求，然不能知出離之法，亦復不知後世因果。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0733c27_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩為彼有情成熟善根，令其堪任法器，乃為開示正道故，成正覺已，詣迦尸國三轉十二行相聖妙法輪。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0734a01_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0734a01_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有有情應以入涅槃相而可度者，菩薩乃為示現入大涅槃。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0734a02_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0734a03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩以是因緣，示現兜率陀天捨壽乃至入大涅槃。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0734a04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0734a04_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即得神通游戲。",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0734a05_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說除蓋障菩薩所問經卷第十一",
        "from": "T14n0489_011:0734a06_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]